{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783806787171,"sessionID":"ses_0acd715bbffezygsvb9LhK73F1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_71NFXqJKQGFGYkoUUSj9YSVO","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"`?\\.opencode/[^` )]+|target_files|Target Files|Files? (?:to|under)","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode","include":"*.md"},"output":"Found 100 matches (more matches available)\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode/003-surface-routing/spec.md:\n  Line 68: ### Files to Change\n\n  Line 72: | `.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-opencode/SKILL.md` | Modify | Detection rule, RUST intent + resource map, CODE_QUALITY registration, reference map, surface non-negotiable |\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode/spec.md:\n  Line 93: ### Files to Change\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode/004-parent-union-drift-guard/spec.md:\n  Line 66: ### Files to Change\n\n  Line 70: | `.opencode/skills/sk-code/shared/references/smart_routing.md` | Modify | Parent RUST union + parent CODE_QUALITY + intent + overlay row |\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode/006-gate-verification-rollup/spec.md:\n  Line 66: ### Files to Change\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode/007-code-opencode-rust-references/spec.md:\n  Line 73: ### Files to Change\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode/005-touchpoints-and-multilang/spec.md:\n  Line 69: ### Files