{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783806787391,"sessionID":"ses_0acd715bbffezygsvb9LhK73F1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_gfO4Oo6tdj9WVqAXygivptAh","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"ps -o command= -p \"$PPID\"","timeout":120000,"workdir":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public"},"output":"opencode run --model openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast --format json --pure --dir /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public --variant high You are orchestrating the deep-review workflow YAML as a detached fan-out lineage.\\012This is an explicit parallel-detached OpenCode lineage, not a self-invocation of the parent session.\\012Use the separate lineage directory and session id below as the detached state boundary.\\012\\012\\012Read .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\\012  spec_folder: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode\\012  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode/review/lineages/gpt56-sol-fast-high\\012  session_id: fanout-gpt56-sol-fast-high-1783806617661-0vtm5z\\012  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\\012  loop_type: review\\012  config.stopPolicy: max-iterations\\012  config.convergenceThreshold: 0.1\\012\\012Review setup bindings (emit before any writes, same as native PRE-BOUND SETUP ANSWERS):\\012review_target: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode\\012review_target_type: spec-folder\\012review_dimensions: all\\012spec_folder: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-code/018-rust-standards-for-code-opencode\\012execution_mode: AUTONOMOUS\\012lineage_mode: auto\\012\\0